text: Silvia Albrecht (born 25 February 1971) is a Swiss badminton player. She competed in women's singles and women's doubles at the 1992 Summer Olympics in Barcelona. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1971 births Category:Living people Category:Swiss female badminton players Category:Olympic badminton players of Switzerland Category:Badminton players at the 1992 Summer Olympics
